---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ScrambleTitle from '../components/ui/ScrambleTitle.svelte';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What I am focusing on now.">
  <article class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <ScrambleTitle client:load text="NOW" tokenId="7184" class="mb-6" />
        <p class="text-muted-foreground animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-100">
          This is my <a href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">now</a> page,
          giving an overview of the things I am doing currently. For finding out more about me,
          you can read <a href="/about" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">about</a>.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose">
        <blockquote>
          Last update was on 24.01.2026
        </blockquote>

        <h3>Building AI powered note-taking setup using ClaudeCode/OpenCode Skills and Obsidian</h3>

        <h3>Making AI Enterprise Accessible</h3>

        <h3>Taking 2x a week Spanish classes on <a href="https://preply.com/en/?pref=ODU5Mjc2Mg==&id=1769239854.453452&ep=" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Preply.com</a></h3>

        <h3>Reading</h3>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13334531-let-s-stay-healthy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            "Let's Stay Healthy"
          </a> by Adelle Davis and
          <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/27220736-shoe-dog" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            "Shoe Dog"
          </a> by Phil Knight
        </p>

        <h3>Trying to work out 3x a week</h3>

        <h3>Enjoying watching my son grow</h3>

        <details class="mt-12">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
            Historical Versions
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">
            <h4>06.05.2025</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Studying AI Agents (i.e. smolagents, ag2, crewai)</li>
              <li>Taking 2x a week spanish language classes on Preply.com</li>
              <li>Embracing the role of being a parent</li>
              <li>Working on smart.AI</li>
              <li>Listening to silence</li>
              <li>Reading: "The Coming Wave" by Mustafa Suleyman and "Creativity.Inc" by Ed Catmull</li>
              <li>Working Out 3x a week</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
